Boasting a sleek and modern exterior in a captivating Blue hue, the 2024 Sonata SEL commands attention wherever it goes. Under the hood, the efficient I4 engine paired with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission and Front-Wheel Drive delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/36 highway MPG.

Carpeted Floor Mats
Cargo Tray
Cargo Side Bins
Rear Bumper Applique

Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, the versatility of a power driver's seat, and the connectivity of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The Sonata SEL's sophisticated cabin is designed with your comfort in mind. Sink into the supportive and heated front bucket seats, surrounded by premium cloth upholstery. The split-folding rear seat offers flexible cargo-carrying capabilities, while the Trunk Cargo Net and Cargo Side Bins help keep your belongings organized and secure.

Hyundai's commitment to safety is evident in the Sonata SEL's comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. Features like Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keeping Assist, and Smart Cruise Control work tirelessly to help you navigate the road with peace of mind.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a road trip, or simply enjoying the daily drive, the 2024 Hyundai Sonata SEL is the perfect companion. With its exceptional value, impressive features, and Hyundai's renowned reliability, this sedan is a must-see for anyone in the market for a refined and capable family car.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility in the 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT. This exceptional SUV is designed to elevate your driving experience, offering a seamless combination of advanced technology, premium comfort, and exceptional efficiency.

Standout features include:

License Plate Front Mounting Package

Indulge in the refined comfort of the Equinox LT, boasting a premium audio system, dual-zone automatic climate control, and heated front seats. Stay connected with the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system, complete with SiriusXM radio and Bluetooth® connectivity.

Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powerful 1.5L DOHC engine, paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, delivering an impressive 24 city / 30 highway MPG. The Equinox's responsive handling and smooth ride quality ensure a truly enjoyable driving experience.

Safety is a top priority, with features like OnStar® emergency communication, dual front airbags, and a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. The Equinox's spacious interior and versatile cargo area make it the perfect companion for your daily commute, weekend adventures, and everything in between.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and practicality.

***918-921-2100***The 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT is a versatile and well-equipped SUV that offers an exceptional driving experience. With its sleek gray exterior, this Equinox is not only stylish but also packed with a range of features that cater to your needs.

LICENSE PLATE FRONT MOUNTING PACKAGE

Under the hood, this Equinox is powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a 6-Speed Automatic Electronic with Overdrive transmission and All-Wheel Drive, delivering a balance of power and efficiency. With an impressive 24 city and 30 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the freedom to explore without constantly stopping for fuel.

The Equinox LT's interior is designed with your comfort in mind. Enjoy the convenience of Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control, Heated Front Seats, and a Power Driver's Seat with 2-Way Power Lumbar Control. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 System with AM/FM radio and SiriusXM will keep you entertained, while the 6-Speaker Audio System and Bluetooth® connectivity ensure you stay connected on the go.

Safety is a top priority in the Equinox LT, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and an Emergency Communication System. The 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS and Electronic Stability Control provide confident handling and control, while the Rear Window Wiper and Variably Intermittent Wipers ensure clear visibility in any weather.

Beyond the impressive list of features, the Equinox LT offers a versatile and spacious interior. The 60/40 Split-Folding Rear Seat allows you to easily accommodate your cargo needs, while the Power Liftgate provides convenient access to the rear storage area.

With a list price of $23,881, this 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT represents an exceptional value in the SUV market. Its combination of style, technology, and functionality make it an ideal choice for those seeking a well-rounded and reliable vehicle.

We invite you to experience the 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT firsthand. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this versatile SUV can enhance your driving experience.

***918-921-2100***Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and performance in the 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT. This exceptional SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and exceed your expectations.

Boasting a sleek white exterior, the Equinox LT commands attention on the road. Under the hood, the 1.5L DOHC engine, paired with a 6-Speed Automatic Electronic transmission, delivers an impressive 26 city/31 highway MPG, making it both efficient and responsive.

License Plate Front Mounting Package

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that caters to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 System with AM/FM radio and SiriusXM, as well as the comfort of heated front seats and a power driver's seat. The Preferred Equipment Group 1LT further enhances your driving experience with features like dual-zone automatic climate control, Bluetooth connectivity, and a premium audio system.

The Equinox LT's versatility is unmatched, with a spacious cabin, split-folding rear seats, and a power liftgate for easy access to the cargo area. Whether you're commuting, running errands, or embarking on a weekend adventure, this SUV is ready to adapt to your lifestyle.

Safety is paramount, and the Equinox LT delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies. From the OnStar emergency communication system to the responsive 4-wheel disc brakes and electronic stability control, you can drive with confidence knowing your protection is a top priority.

Discover the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of the 2024 Chevrolet Equinox LT. Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and performance that will elevate your driving experience. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can enhance your life on the road.

description: Discover the 2025 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE: A Perfect Blend of Efficiency, Style, and Safety for the Modern Driver Seeking a Reliable and Eco-Friendly Commute. Step into the future of driving with the 2025 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE, a vehicle meticulously crafted for those who value both sustainability and style. This used model, adorned in a striking Ruby Flare Pearl, offers an impressive hybrid powertrain that pairs a 4-cylinder engine with a lithium-ion traction battery, ensuring a smooth and efficient ride. The Corolla Hybrid LE is designed for the discerning driver who appreciates advanced safety features. With Automatic Highbeams, Lane Departure Warning, and Front Collision Mitigation, you can navigate with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected. The Corolla Hybrid LE s interior is equally impressive, featuring Smart Device Integration and a WiFi Hotspot to keep you connected on the go. Adaptive Cruise Control and Cruise Control Steering Assist make long drives more comfortable, while the Back-Up Camera and Cross-Traffic Alert enhance your parking experience. Enjoy the convenience of Keyless Start and Remote Trunk Release, and revel in the clarity of LED Headlights during nighttime journeys. The 2025 Toyota Corolla Hybrid LE is more than just a car it s a companion for the eco-conscious driver who refuses to compromise on performance or style. Be sure to call or visit Toyota of Richardson to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description: Discover the 2025 Toyota Corolla LE: A Compact Marvel with Advanced Safety and Smart Connectivity for the Modern Driver Step into the future with the 2025 Toyota Corolla LE, a used gem that perfectly balances practicality and innovation. Designed for those who appreciate the reliability of a Toyota Corolla, this compact car offers an array of features tailored for the modern driver. The sleek Ruby Flare Pearl exterior turns heads, while its efficient 4-cylinder engine coupled with a smooth CVT transmission ensures a responsive and enjoyable drive. Safety is paramount with the Corolla LE, equipped with cutting-edge features like Automatic Highbeams, Lane Departure Warning, and Front Collision Mitigation, providing peace of mind on every journey. The Cross-Traffic Alert and Evasion Assist further enhance your driving confidence, making city and highway driving a breeze. Inside, the Corolla LE boasts smart connectivity with Bluetooth, a WiFi Hotspot, and Smart Device Integration, keeping you connected and entertained on the go. Adaptive Cruise Control and Cruise Control Steering Assist make long drives more comfortable, while the Back-Up Camera ensures parking is effortless. The Corolla LE is not just a car it s a trusted companion for your daily adventures, offering a seamless blend of technology, safety, and style. Be sure to call or visit Toyota of Richardson to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

Our extensive inventory features rigorously inspected Hyundai CPO models like the Elantra, Sonata, Tucson, Santa Fe, and more that come with extended warranty coverage, roadside assistance, and peace of mind from Hyundai's strict certification process. We also offer a wide selection of dependable used cars, trucks, and SUVs from various trusted brands, all thoroughly checked by our certified technicians for safety, reliability, and performance. With fresh arrivals and competitive pricing, you're sure to find the perfect fit for your budget and lifestyle. Enjoy attractive **specials and offers** on pre-owned vehicles, including low APR financing options (such as 2.99% for qualified buyers on select CPO models), Manager's Specials, and limited-time promotions that maximize your savings. Our no-pressure, knowledgeable team is dedicated to your satisfaction, guiding you through financing and beyond. description:
Designed for happier days, our 2026 Honda Civic LX Sedan delivers the goods in Crystal Black Pearl! Powered by a 2.0 Liter 4 Cylinder supplying 150hp to a CVT with a dedicated ECON mode for enhanced efficiency. This Front Wheel Drive sedan achieves nearly 41mpg on the highway and has agile handling for when life throws you a curve. Upscale details upgrade our Civic exterior, which features LED lighting, power mirrors, and aggressively crafted lines. It's a bold design that doesn't hold back!

Our LX cabin is command central, providing comfortable cloth seats, a folding back row, a multifunction steering wheel, automatic climate control, keyless access, pushbutton ignition, a 12V outlet, and clever cargo solutions for keeping organized. A 7-inch touchscreen and 7-inch driver display can keep connections close with Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, Bluetooth, and a four-speaker audio system for your favorite soundtrack.

It's hard to know what the road will bring next. Still, Honda helps you stay prepared with automatic braking, adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assistance, forward collision warning, a multi-angle rearview camera, tire pressure monitoring, hill start assist, and more. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility with the 2026 Chevrolet Trax LT. This dynamic compact SUV is designed to elevate your driving experience and meet the demands of your active lifestyle.

Tailored to your preferences, this Trax LT comes equipped with a host of premium features, including:

LT Convenience Package: Keyless Open, Heated Seats, Heated Steering Wheel, Wrapped Steering Wheel, and Heated Power-Adjustable Mirrors
Interior Protection Package: Cargo Liner and All-Weather Floor Liners

Powered by the efficient ECOTEC 1.2L Turbo engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 6-Speed Automatic transmission, the Trax LT delivers an exceptional balance of power and fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 28 city/32 highway MPG.

Step inside the spacious, well-appointed cabin and discover the thoughtful design elements that make the Trax LT a true standout. The Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system with wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained, while the available heated front seats and steering wheel provide welcomed comfort on chilly days.

Versatility is at the heart of the Trax LT, with a split-folding rear seat and ample cargo space to accommodate your active lifestyle. Whether you're embarking on a weekend getaway or navigating the daily commute, this compact SUV offers the perfect balance of style, functionality, and efficiency.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2026 Chevrolet Trax LT. Visit our showroom today and let our team of experts guide you through the features and capabilities that make this vehicle the perfect fit for your needs.

description:
The 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT is a versatile and well-equipped SUV that offers a compelling blend of style, technology, and performance. With its sleek white exterior and a host of impressive features, this Equinox is poised to elevate your driving experience.

This Equinox comes equipped with a robust 1.5L DOHC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, delivering an efficient 26 city/28 highway MPG. Enjoy the convenience of the Navigation System, the premium audio experience of the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system, and the added comfort of the Heated Steering Wheel and Heated Front Seats. Stay connected with the SiriusXM w/360L Trial Subscription, and stay safe with the advanced safety features, including the Emergency Communication System, Dual Front Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control.

Navigation System

Rear window defroster

The Equinox LT's sleek and modern design, combined with its impressive list of features, makes it a compelling choice for those seeking a versatile and well-equipped SUV. With its spacious interior, flexible seating, and ample cargo capacity, this Equinox is ready to accommodate your everyday needs and weekend adventures.

Experience the confidence and convenience of the 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can enhance your driving experience.

SPORTY STYLE WITH SMART URBAN PERFORMANCE

FINISHED IN WHITE SANDS WITH A JET BLACK INTERIOR FEATURING GRAY WITH RED ACCENTS, THIS TRAX 1RS DELIVERS A SPORT-INSPIRED LOOK THAT STANDS OUT IN CITY TRAFFIC OR ON THE OPEN ROAD. POWERED BY A 1.2L ECOTEC TURBO ENGINE PAIRED WITH A 6-SPEED AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSION, THE TRAX OFFERS RESPONSIVE ACCELERATION AND EXCELLENT FUEL EFFICIENCY FOR DAILY DRIVING.

PERFORMANCE & EFFICIENCY

THE 1.2L TURBO ENGINE PROVIDES A GREAT BALANCE OF POWER AND EFFICIENCY, MAKING THE TRAX 1RS IDEAL FOR COMMUTING, ERRANDS, AND WEEKEND GETAWAYS. ITS COMPACT SIZE AND AGILE HANDLING MAKE IT EASY TO MANEUVER IN TIGHT SPACES, WHILE A SMOOTH-SHIFTING AUTOMATIC TRANSMISSION ENSURES A COMFORTABLE AND CONFIDENT DRIVE. MULTIPLE DRIVE MODES HELP OPTIMIZE PERFORMANCE FOR DIFFERENT ROAD CONDITIONS.

INTERIOR & TECHNOLOGY

INSIDE, THE TRAX 1RS FEATURES A MODERN CABIN DESIGNED AROUND DRIVER CONVENIENCE AND CONNECTIVITY. SPORT-INSPIRED SEATING, A FLAT-BOTTOM STEERING WHEEL, AND CONTRAST RED ACCENTS CREATE AN ENERGETIC ATMOSPHERE. TECHNOLOGY HIGHLIGHTS INCLUDE A LARGE TOUCHSCREEN INFOTAINMENT SYSTEM WITH WIRELESS APPLE CARPLAY AND ANDROID AUTO, A DIGITAL DRIVER INFORMATION DISPLAY, WIRELESS PHONE CONNECTIVITY, AND MULTIPLE USB PORTS TO KEEP EVERYONE CONNECTED ON THE GO.

EXTERIOR DESIGN

THE 1RS TRIM ADDS A BOLD EDGE TO THE TRAX WITH BLACK EXTERIOR ACCENTS, UNIQUE 1RS BADGING, SPORTY WHEELS, AND A DISTINCTIVE FRONT GRILLE. LED LIGHTING ENHANCES VISIBILITY WHILE ADDING TO THE VEHICLES MODERN, ATHLETIC APPEARANCE. ROOF RAILS AND A COMPACT PROFILE ADD BOTH STYLE AND PRACTICALITY FOR EVERYDAY USE.

SAFETY & DRIVER ASSISTANCE

CHEVY SAFETY ASSIST COMES STANDARD AND INCLUDES AUTOMATIC EMERGENCY BRAKING, FORWARD COLLISION ALERT, FRONT PEDESTRIAN BRAKING, LANE KEEP ASSIST WITH LANE DEPARTURE WARNING, FOLLOWING DISTANCE INDICATOR, AND INTELLIBEAM AUTOMATIC HIGH BEAMS. ADDITIONAL FEATURES SUCH AS A REAR VISION CAMERA AND AVAILABLE ADVANCED SAFETY TECHNOLOGIES PROVIDE CONFIDENCE BEHIND THE WHEEL.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT, a versatile and well-equipped SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience. This stunning White Equinox LT boasts a 1.5L DOHC engine, paired with a smooth-shifting CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, delivering an impressive 26 city/28 highway MPG.

Packed with a comprehensive array of premium features, this Equinox LT is designed to cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of the Navigation System, the clarity of the 11.3" Diagonal Advanced Color LCD Display, and the seamless integration of the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 system with SiriusXM w/360L Trial Subscription. Stay connected and entertained with the 6 Speakers and the AM/FM radio.

Comfort is a top priority in this Equinox LT, with features like Heated Driver & Front Passenger Seats, a Heated Steering Wheel, and Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control. The Cloth Seat Trim and Front Bucket Seats provide a refined and supportive driving experience, while the Split Folding Rear Seat offers versatility for your cargo needs.

Safety is also a key focus, with a suite of advanced technologies including Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Overhead Airbag, Occupant Sensing Airbag, and Electronic Stability Control. The Emergency Communication System with OnStar and Chevrolet Connected Services provides added peace of mind.

Exterior features like the Body-Color Bumpers, Heated Power Door Mirrors, and Spoiler enhance the Equinox LT's sleek and modern appearance, while the 17" Grazen Metallic Machined-Face Aluminum Wheels add a touch of style.

This 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT is priced at $25,269, making it an exceptional value proposition in the compact SUV segment. Experience the perfect balance of performance, technology, and style by visiting our showroom and taking this remarkable Equinox LT for a test drive. We're confident you'll be impressed by its uncompromising quality and versatility.

The 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT is a remarkable compact SUV that offers exceptional value and a wealth of premium features. With its sleek black exterior and advanced 1.5L DOHC engine paired with a smooth CVT transmission and front-wheel drive, this Equinox delivers a dynamic and efficient driving experience.

Key features of this well-equipped Equinox LT include:

Navigation System
6 Speakers
SiriusXM w/360L Trial Subscription
Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Premium Audio System
Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
Heated Steering Wheel
Heated Front Seats
Rear Window Defroster
Power Windows and Doors
Remote Keyless Entry
Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls

The Equinox LT's impressive array of technology and comfort amenities elevates the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the large 11.3" color touchscreen display, seamless smartphone integration, and the peace of mind provided by advanced safety features like Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keep Assist, and OnStar emergency services.

Beyond its well-appointed interior, the Equinox LT delivers exceptional versatility. The split-folding rear seats and generous cargo space make it easy to accommodate your evolving lifestyle, whether you're transporting bulky items, sports gear, or your growing family. And with an EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this Equinox LT offers impressive fuel efficiency to help you save at the pump.

Crafted with meticulous attention to detail and backed by Chevrolet's renowned reputation for quality, the 2026 Equinox LT is a compelling choice for those seeking a compact SUV that seamlessly blends style, technology, and practicality. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by all that this exceptional Equinox has to offer.

With a list price of $24,944, the 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT represents an outstanding value in the compact SUV segment. Visit our showroom to explore this vehicle in person and discover why the Equinox should be at the top of your shopping list.

description: This New 2026 Volkswagen Jetta S is finished in Pure White with a Titan Black interior. Stock number V26659. To check availability or schedule a test drive, call  . Shoppers looking for a new Volkswagen in the Naperville and Chicagoland area will appreciate this models features, performance, and value. Every new Volkswagen purchased at Bill Jacobs Volkswagen includes Bill Jacobs Total Protection, our complimentary 7 Year/100,000 mile Limited Powertrain Warranty that gives you long-term confidence and added peace of mind. Important Package and Feature Information Convenience Unresponsive driver assistant - a reaction to inaction. Maybe you fell asleep. Maybe you lost consciousness. No matter how it happens, Unresponsive driver assistant works to help lessen the danger when it does. It detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness, automatically bringing the vehicle to a stop and turning on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will also be contacted. Unresponsive driver assistant is safety that never sleeps.Safety and Security Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down; speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control. Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.Technology and Telematics Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road. At Bill Jacobs Volkswagen, we are here to serve you with a straightforward and transparent car buying experience. Whether you are comparing new car prices, researching features, or scheduling a test drive, our team is dedicated to guiding you with accurate information and real-time market data. Financing Options Our dealership partners with leading Credit Unions and National Banks to provide competitive low-rate financing for most credit levels. We create customized financing packages that match your goals. To save time at the dealership, complete our secure online credit application before your visit.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2026 Chevrolet Equinox LT. description:
Discover the exceptional 2026 Toyota Corolla LE, a sedan that seamlessly blends style, performance, and cutting-edge technology. This meticulously maintained vehicle, with only 7 miles on the odometer, is a true gem waiting to be uncovered.

Boasting a sleek beige exterior and a spacious, well-appointed interior, the Corolla LE is designed to elevate your driving experience. Key features include:

All Weather Floor Liner Package
LE Premium Package
6 Speakers
8" Toyota Audio Multimedia System
Automatic Climate Control
Remote Keyless Entry
Traction Control
Smart Key System
Rear Bumper Protector
Apple CarPlay/Android Auto Integration

Under the hood, the Corolla LE is powered by a 2.0L I4 PDI DOHC 16V engine, delivering an impressive 169 horsepower and exceptional fuel efficiency of 32 city/41 highway MPG. The Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) and Front-Wheel Drive (FWD) configuration ensure a smooth, responsive, and efficient driving experience.

Safety is paramount in the Corolla LE, with a comprehensive suite of advanced features, including ABS brakes, dual front and side impact airbags, Electronic Stability Control, and Rear Camera Assist. The Smart Key System and Panic Alarm provide added peace of mind, while the Auto High-Beam Headlights and Delay-Off Headlights enhance visibility and safety, regardless of driving conditions.

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, the Corolla LE boasts a wealth of premium amenities, such as Heated Power Door Mirrors, Telescoping Steering Wheel, and Tilt Steering Wheel. The Fabric Seat Trim, Front Bucket Seats, and Split Folding Rear Seat ensure a comfortable and versatile interior for you and your passengers.

This exceptional 2026 Toyota Corolla LE is a testament to the brand's commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Corolla LE's exceptional value and performance.

description:
Here are good reasons people choose to buy a new 2026 Hyundai Elantra SEL Sport especially if you want a practical, stylish, and well-equipped compact sedan without paying for higher trims: 1. Strong Value for the Price The SEL Sport starts around ~$23,750 MSRP a competitive price in the compact sedan segment. It delivers a solid mix of essential features without pushing into premium pricing. 2. Practical and Efficient Powered by a 2.0-liter 4-cylinder (147 hp) with a smooth automatic transmission, the SEL Sport balances performance and efficiency about 30 mpg city / 40 mpg highway. Its ideal for daily commuting, errands, and highway cruising without feeling underpowered. 3. Sporty Styling Without Extra Cost Sport-oriented exterior cues include gloss-black 17 wheels, black mirror caps, and a rear spoiler giving a more aggressive look vs the base SE. Inside, you get things like metallic pedals and a leather-wrapped steering wheel/shift knob, which add a fun and more engaging feel. 4. Good Tech and Connectivity Standard tech includes an 8 touchscreen, Apple CarPlay & Android Auto (wireless), and wireless phone charging, which is impressive for this trim level. You also get dual USB ports and essential modern conveniences that make everyday use easy. 5. Excellent Safety Package Even on SEL Sport, the Elantra comes with Hyundais SmartSense driver-assist suite forward collision-avoidance, blind-spot warning, rear cross-traffic assist, and more. The Elantra family earns top safety ratings, which speaks to strong occupant protection. 6. Big Warranty Hyundais warranty remains one of the best: typically 5 yr/60,000 mi basic and 10 yr/100,000 mi powertrain coverage, plus roadside assistance. That means long-term peace of mind and often lower ownership risk vs some rivals. 7. Roomy and Comfortable Despite being a compact sedan, the Elantra offers competitive interior space with good passenger room and trunk capacity for its class. Priced below KBB Fair Purchase Price! 30/39 City/Highway MPG 2026 Hyundai Elantra SEL Sport

This 2026 Honda Civic Sport represents an exceptional value in the pre-owned market. With its combination of performance, technology, and safety features, it's the perfect choice for the driver who demands more from their vehicle. Don't miss your chance to experience the Civic's renowned reliability and driver-focused design. Schedule a test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2026 Toyota Corolla LE. This exceptional sedan offers a seamless blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Boasting a robust 2.0L I4 engine with 169 horsepower, the Corolla LE delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience, complemented by its impressive fuel efficiency of 32 city/41 highway MPG. Enjoy the convenience of the continuously variable transmission (CVT) and the confidence of front-wheel drive, ensuring a comfortable and efficient ride every time.

6 Speakers
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
Radio data system
Radio: 8" Toyota Audio Multimedia
Air Conditioning
Automatic temperature control
Rear window defroster
Power steering
Power windows
Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
Traction control
4-Wheel Disc Brakes
ABS brakes

The Corolla LE's exterior shines in a sleek White finish, complemented by body-color bumpers and heated, power-adjustable side mirrors for added convenience. Step inside and discover a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium fabric seating, a front center armrest, and a split-folding rear seat for versatile cargo-carrying capabilities.

Safety is a top priority in the Corolla LE, with an impressive array of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Automatic High-Beam Headlights, Rear Camera, and Toyota Safety Sense, providing you with the peace of mind you deserve on the road.

Elevate your driving experience and make the 2026 Toyota Corolla LE your own. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why this exceptional sedan should be at the top of your list.

description:
Introducing the 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT, the ultimate truck for those who demand power, performance, and luxury. With its rugged exterior and premium features, this truck stands out from the rest.

Under the hood, the 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT boasts a powerful 5.3L V8 engine, capable of producing 355 horsepower and 383 lb-ft of torque. Whether you're hauling heavy loads or tackling tough terrain, this truck has the strength to handle it all.

Step inside the spacious and luxurious cabin, where you'll find premium leather seats and a state-of-the-art infotainment system. Stay connected on the go with Bluetooth connectivity and access your favorite apps with ease.

But it's not just about luxury, the 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT also offers impressive towing and hauling capabilities, making it the perfect workhorse for any job. Plus, with its advanced safety features, you can have peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this impressive truck. Come test drive the 2014 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT today and experience the power, performance, and luxury for yourself.

Take our 2014 Toyota 4Runner SR5 shown in Nautical Blue Pearl out for a spin! Powered by a 4.0 Liter V6 that offers 270hp connected to a 5 Speed Automatic transmission for easy passing maneuvers. This Rear Wheel Drive SUV scores nearly 22mpg on the highway, whether tackling trails or gliding through the carpool lane, delivering rugged off-road capabilities with a smooth, quiet ride. This SR5 has a fresh, bold look with 17-inch wheels and a roof rack.


Step inside our SR5 and notice soft-touch door trim and a leather-wrapped steering wheel. Entune infotainment, Bluetooth®, and an eight-speaker audio system with available satellite radio and iPod connectivity keep you entertained and connected. A 40/20/40 split seat offers versatility and reclines for additional comfort in the rear. Amazingly, the rear window opens, which is great for ventilation and loading groceries!


Whatever your adventure, you'll be prepared and safe thanks to Toyota's ABS and an army of airbags. You can load it up with gear, put a bike rack on the back, put a cargo box on the rack, tow your trailer, and still seat all your friends comfortably in this 4Runner SR5. description:
Introducing the 2014 Toyota Tundra SR the truck that's as tough as your Uncle Bob after a few too many BBQ ribs! This beauty is powered by a robust 5.7L V8 engine that delivers a whopping 381 horsepower and a tire-squealing 401 ft-lbs of torque. That's right, folks, this Tundra can tow your boat, haul your lumber, and still have enough muscle left to outrun your neighbor's yappy dog!

Dressed in a pristine Super White exterior, this truck is cleaner than your last attempt at a home-cooked meal and we all know how that turned out! The Graphite leather interior is so comfortable, you might just find yourself taking a nap in the driver's seat instead of getting out when you reach your destination. (We don't condone sleeping on the job, but we understand the temptation!)

Now, let's talk features because this Tundra is not just a pretty face. It comes equipped with a full suite of factory default options, including:

- A spacious cabin that could double as a mini living room for those long road trips (snacks not included).
- Bluetooth connectivity to keep you hands-free while you belt out your favorite karaoke tunes just remember, the truck doesn't judge, but your passengers might!
- A touchscreen infotainment system that's easier to navigate than your GPS when it's trying to avoid traffic.
- Backup camera, because who needs to play a game of "guess what's behind me" when you can have a high-def view instead?
- Plenty of storage compartments for all your gear, from tools to snacks because let's face it, snacks are essential for any adventure.

Fuel efficiency? Well, this Tundra gets a respectable 13 MPG in the city and 18 MPG on the highway. While it may not be winning any eco-friendly awards, it sure knows how to carry your gear with style and power!

This vehicle is in excellent overall condition, has a clean CARFAX report, and has had only one owner. That means it's like finding the last piece of pizza

description:
Introducing the 2018 Honda Civic Si: the car that proves you can have your cake and drive it too! With a zippy 1.5L Turbo I4 engine pumping out a lively 205 horsepower and a delightful 192 ft-lbs of torque, this little beauty doesn't just take you places it invites you to enjoy the ride.

Draped in a stunning Lunar Silver Metallic exterior, this Civic Si is like the stylish friend who always shows up looking effortlessly chic. It's the kind of car that says, I mean business while also whispering, Let's have some fun! And let's not forget about the interior featuring sleek black cloth seats that are as comfortable as your favorite pair of sweatpants (but way more socially acceptable to wear in public).

Now, let's talk about fuel efficiency. With an impressive 28 MPG in the city and a whopping 38 MPG on the highway, this Civic Si is the ultimate money-saving machine. You can spend less time at the pump and more time cruising the streets, pretending you're in a high-speed car chase (without the actual danger, of course).

This vehicle is in excellent overall condition, which means it's been treated better than most house pets no scratching or drooling here! Plus, it comes with a clean CARFAX report, so you can hit the road with peace of mind, knowing that this Civic has no skeletons hiding in its trunk.

So, if you're ready to elevate your driving experience with a car that's as fun as a roller coaster ride (minus the nausea), the 2018 Honda Civic Si is here, waiting to be your new partner-in-crime. Buckle up and get ready to turn heads!

description:
===== 2019 Ford Ranger XLT for sale near Sacramento CA =====





This 2019 Ford Ranger XLT proves that good things come in the right size, not just the biggest size. If you are searching for a midsize pickup that fits in parking spots but still works hard, this Ranger is ready to impress. Drivers across Sacramento, Woodland, Roseville, Elk Grove, and the Bay Area love the Ranger because it balances daily comfort with real truck capability. It is the kind of truck that handles weekday errands and weekend projects without breaking a sweat.





==== Why This Ranger Stands Out ====





The Ford Ranger XLT is known for smart design, confident road manners, and a reputation for reliability. It is easy to drive, easy to live with, and still looks good pulling up to a job site or a trailhead. This model earned recognition as one of the ten favorite cars of its model year, which says a lot considering how many vehicles compete for attention.





==== Ownership Benefits ====





This Ranger comes with Hoblit Select Shield, giving you a three month and three thousand mile powertrain warranty for extra peace of mind. That means you can focus on enjoying the drive instead of worrying about surprises.





==== Why Buy from Hoblit Dodge ====





Hoblit Dodge has been family owned since nineteen forty nine and is proudly located in historic downtown Woodland. Our small town handshake style means honest answers, friendly service, and no pressure. As the number one Ram Truck dealership in California, we proudly serve Sacramento, Folsom, Roseville, Elk Grove, the Bay Area, Reno, Tahoe, Yuba City, Colusa, and all of California.





==== Call Us Today ====





Call Hoblit Dodge now to schedule a test drive of this 2019 Ford Ranger XLT or to ask any questions you may have. Trucks like this do not stay available for long. Pick up the phone today and see why this Ranger is a favorite for drivers who want versatility with a sense of humor.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, performance, and efficiency in this 2020 Ford Fusion SE. With its sleek black exterior and a host of premium features, this Fusion is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Alloy wheels
SYNC 3 Communications & Entertainment System
Dual-zone automatic climate control
Power driver's seat
Rear-view camera
Keyless entry with remote start

Powered by a 1.5L EcoBoost engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 6-speed automatic transmission, this Fusion delivers an impressive 23 mpg in the city and 34 mpg on the highway, making it an exceptional choice for the daily commute or weekend getaways.

Beyond its efficient powertrain, the Fusion SE boasts a wealth of advanced technologies and conveniences to enhance your driving experience. The SYNC 3 infotainment system seamlessly integrates with your smartphone, allowing you to stay connected on the go. Dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone on board enjoys their ideal temperature, while the power driver's seat provides exceptional comfort and support.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, electronic stability control, and a suite of airbags to help protect you and your passengers. The rear-view camera makes backing up a breeze, and the keyless entry with remote start adds an extra layer of convenience.

With its sleek styling, efficient powertrain, and impressive list of features, this 2020 Ford Fusion SE is the perfect blend of performance, technology, and value. Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Fusion's exceptional qualities and eager to make it your next automotive companion.

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, capability, and convenience in the 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LT. This exceptional SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience with its impressive list of premium features and thoughtful design.

Confidence & Convenience Package
Infotainment Package
Wheels, 18 Aluminum
Remote Start
Rear Power Liftgate
Heated Driver & Front Passenger Seats
HD Rear Vision Camera
Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert
Rear Cross Traffic Alert
Rear Park Assist with Audible Warning
Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
120-Volt Power Outlet
2 USB Data Ports with SD Card Reader

The Equinox LT's striking Cajun Red Tintcoat exterior commands attention, while the spacious and well-appointed interior offers the perfect blend of comfort and technology. Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, remote start, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM Radio. The available Confidence & Convenience Package and Infotainment Package further elevate your driving experience with advanced safety features and seamless connectivity.

Powered by a 1.5L DOHC engine and paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, this all-wheel-drive Equinox delivers a dynamic and efficient performance. With an EPA-estimated 25 city/30 highway MPG, you can confidently tackle your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Versatility is at the heart of the Equinox LT, with a spacious cargo area and split-folding rear seats that allow you to adapt to your needs. The rear power liftgate and available hands-free liftgate make loading and unloading a breeze.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like the HD Rear Vision Camera, Lane Change Alert with Side Blind Zone Alert, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert keeping you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Experience the perfect balance of style, capability, and technology in the 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LT. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional SUV for a test drive and discover how it can elevate your driving experience.

description:
===== 2020 Dodge Charger GT for sale near Woodland CA =====





This 2020 Dodge Charger GT proves that a sedan can still have attitude. If you are searching for a sporty Dodge Charger for sale near Sacramento that looks fast even when parked, this one checks that box with confidence and a little swagger.





==== Bold style that does not whisper ====





The Blacktop Package delivers a sharp and aggressive look from every angle. Satin black badges, a black one piece performance spoiler, and twenty inch black noise painted wheels make this Charger look like it already knows where it is going. The black cloth interior keeps things simple, comfortable, and ready for daily driving or weekend fun.





==== Popular features buyers look for online ====






Black cloth interior
Blacktop Package
Black one piece performance spoiler
Black badge
Black Dodge grille badge
Gloss black instrument panel cluster trim rings
Quick Order Package Two EH
Satin black Charger decklid badge
Satin black Dodge tail lamp badge
Twenty inch by eight inch black noise painted wheels






==== Confidence included with Hoblit Select Shield ====





This Dodge Charger GT comes with Hoblit Select Shield which includes a three Month three thousand Mile Powertrain Warranty. That means added peace of mind while enjoying every mile behind the wheel.





==== Why drivers choose Hoblit Dodge ====





Hoblit Dodge has been family owned since 1949 in Historic Downtown Woodland. We are proud to serve Sacramento, Elk Grove, Folsom, Roseville, the Bay Area, Reno, Tahoe, Yuba City, Colusa, and all of California. Our handshake style approach means friendly service, clear answers, and no pressure.





==== Call today and drive it home ====





Call Hoblit Dodge today to schedule a test drive or ask questions about this 2020 Dodge Charger GT. Vehicles with this look and personality do not last long. Call now and see how fun your daily drive can be.

<p>Experience the Thrill of the 2021 Kia Soul GT-Line: A Bold Ride for the Adventurous Spirit</p>
<p>Step into the captivating world of the 2021 Kia Soul GT-Line, where style meets performance in a package designed for those who crave excitement. Dressed in a striking Neptune Blue, this 4D hatchback is not just a car; it's a statement. Under the hood, the 2.0L I4 MPI DOHC 16V engine delivers a spirited 147 horsepower, ensuring every drive is a dynamic experience. The CVT transmission offers seamless gear shifts, providing both efficiency and a smooth ride.</p>
<p>Inside, the GT-Line trim elevates the Soul's interior with sport-inspired touches, including a leather-wrapped steering wheel and unique upholstery, making every journey feel like a special occasion. The intuitive infotainment system, complete with a vibrant touchscreen, keeps you connected and entertained, whether you're navigating city streets or embarking on a weekend getaway.</p>
<p>Safety is paramount, and the 2021 Kia Soul GT-Line is equipped with advanced features like blind-spot monitoring and lane-keeping assist, offering peace of mind on every adventure. With its bold design, exhilarating performance, and innovative technology, this used Kia Soul GT-Line is the perfect companion for those who live life on their own terms.</p>

description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and style with this 2021 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid Blue. This exceptional vehicle offers an unbeatable combination of advanced technology, impressive fuel economy, and a sleek, modern design.

THIS VEHICLE ALSO INCLUDES THE FOLLOWING OPTIONS AND FEATURES:

Carpeted Floor Mats
Reversible Cargo Tray
Rear Bumper Applique
Wheel Locks
Cargo Net
Option Group 01

Boasting an impressive 49 MPG in the city and 52 MPG on the highway, this Elantra Hybrid Blue delivers exceptional fuel efficiency without compromising performance. Powered by a 1.6L I4 DGI Hybrid DOHC 16V engine paired with a 6-Speed EcoShift Dual Clutch transmission, this vehicle provides a smooth and responsive driving experience.

Beyond its impressive powertrain, this Elantra Hybrid Blue is packed with a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the comfort of heated front seats, the convenience of an exterior parking camera, and the enhanced audio experience of 6 premium speakers. The alloy wheels add a touch of sophistication, while the carpeted floor mats and reversible cargo tray provide practical solutions for your everyday needs.

Thoughtfully designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, this Elantra Hybrid Blue offers a host of advanced technologies. From the AM/FM radio with SiriusXM and Display Audio system to the automatic temperature control and power windows, this vehicle is equipped to make every drive a pleasure.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, dual front impact airbags, and an emergency communication system to give you peace of mind on the road.

Experience the perfect blend of efficiency, technology, and style with this 2021 Hyundai Elantra Hybrid Blue. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional vehicle for a test drive and discover why it's the perfect choice for your next ride.

===== 2022 Jeep Compass Trailhawk for Sale Near Sacramento CA =====





This 2022 Jeep Compass Trailhawk is built for drivers who want a compact SUV that feels confident in daily traffic and genuinely capable when the road turns rough. It combines true Jeep Trailhawk toughness with a size that is easy to live with, making it a strong choice for commuting, weekend exploring, and everything in between across Sacramento and Northern California.





==== Trailhawk Capability in a Practical Size ====





The Compass Trailhawk is designed for drivers who want more than just all wheel traction. With four wheel drive and Trailhawk specific off road tuning, it is engineered to handle uneven terrain, changing weather, and spontaneous detours without hesitation. If you are searching for a 2022 Jeep Compass Trailhawk for sale near Woodland, Sacramento, Roseville, or the Bay Area, this SUV offers real Jeep capability in a manageable footprint.





==== Features Buyers Search For ====






Four wheel drive capability
Quick Order Package 2GE
Trailhawk off road focused design
Confident all weather performance






= === Built for Everyday Driving and Weekend Escapes ====





This Compass Trailhawk is easy to maneuver in city traffic and parking lots, yet ready when the road points toward Tahoe, back roads, or less traveled routes. It is the kind of SUV that fits daily life while still encouraging you to take the long way home.





==== Hoblit Select Shield Protection ====





This Jeep Compass includes Hoblit Select Shield coverage with a three month three thousand mile powertrain warranty. That added protection provides extra peace of mind from the first drive forward.





==== Why Drivers Choose Hoblit Dodge ====





Hoblit Dodge has been family owned since 1949 and is located in Historic Downtown Woodland. As the number one Ram truck dealership in California, we are known for honest answers, a relaxed buying experience, and service that still values a handshake. We proudly serve drivers from Sacramento, Elk Grove, Folsom, Roseville, the Bay Area, Reno, Tahoe, Yuba City, Colusa, and across Northern California.





==== Schedule Your Test Drive ====





If you are looking for a 2022 Jeep Compass Trailhawk for sale near Sacramento CA, this one deserves a closer look. Call Hoblit Dodge today to schedule a test drive or get more details before it is gone.

description:
Unveiling the vibrant 2024 Hyundai Venue Limited in a striking Intense Blue finish. This compact 4D Sport Utility is designed to make urban adventures and daily commutes both fun and efficient. With a clean CARFAX and its fantastic fuel economy of 29/33 City/Highway MPG from its I4 engine and smooth CVT transmission, this Venue is a smart and stylish choice for anyone looking for a modern ride. Its the perfect blend of small-car maneuverability and SUV-like convenience, making it a standout in its class.

Inside, the Venue Limited is all about comfort and technology. You'll stay cozy on cold days with Heated Front Bucket Seats, while the Automatic temperature control keeps the climate just right. The cabin feels premium with a Leather steering wheel and a Leather Shift Knob, making every touch point feel a little more special. It's a surprisingly roomy space for its size, with plenty of headroom and a design that feels open and airy.

Staying connected and entertained is effortless. The Navigation System is ready to guide you to your next destination, while Apple CarPlay & Android Auto seamlessly integrate your smartphone for easy access to your apps, music, and messages. All of this is controlled through the user-friendly AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM w/Navigation System radio and the convenient Steering wheel mounted audio controls, so you can keep your focus on the road ahead.

Safety and convenience are key features of this Hyundai. Auto High-beam Headlights and Fully automatic headlights adjust to the conditions, providing excellent visibility. The Emergency communication system and Security system offer peace of mind on every journey. Plus, with a Rear window wiper, Power door mirrors, and Heated door mirrors, this Venue is equipped to handle a variety of weather conditions with ease.

This 2024 Hyundai Venue Limited offers a fantastic value proposition, packing a great list of features into a compact, agile, and fuel-efficient package. Its stylish design, high-tech interior, and practical nature make it a perfect companion for city living and beyond. It's a testament to how an affordable vehicle can still deliver on modern expectations for comfort, convenience, and safety.

description:
Elevate your drive with our One Owner 2024 Toyota Corolla LE Sedan in Ice Cap! Motivated by a 2.0 Liter 4 Cylinder providing 169hp to a CVT for keeping up with busy days. Known for its agile handling, this Front Wheel Drive sedan achieves nearly 41mpg on the highway with an athletic design. Our Corolla commands the road with LED lighting, a sport black grille, and an aggressive stance. Toyota hit a home run with this bold appearance!


You can turn to our LE cabin for a comfortable environment and modern convenience. The premium fabric seats include a folding second row for extra versatility, as well as a multifunction steering wheel, automatic climate control, power accessories, keyless access, a front center console, and a 4.2-inch driver display for key vehicle systems. Your mobile command center incorporates an 8-inch touchscreen, wireless Apple CarPlay®/Android Auto®, WiFi compatibility, Bluetooth®, voice command, and a six-speaker sound system. There's ample space to spread out and relax, too.


Toyota's Proactive Driving Assist can help reduce your stress behind the wheel, backed by automatic braking, adaptive cruise control, forward collision warning, lane-departure alert, pedestrian detection, a rearview camera, and more. Easy to own, our Corolla LE sedan is a fuel-efficient, fun machine! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

description:
You're sure to love our One Owner 2024 Nissan Altima SV Sedan that's bold and expressive in Brilliant Silver Metallic! Motivated by a 2.5 Liter 4 Cylinder delivering 188hp tethered to an Xtronic CVT for a top-notch driving experience. This Front Wheel Drive sedan supplies comfortable handling and confident acceleration, and it can see nearly 39mpg on the highway. Seeing our Altima is a treat since it features strong lines, LED lighting, a body-color rear diffuser, alloy wheels, chrome door handles, and black mirror caps.


Slide inside our comfortable SV cabin that greets you with features like supportive cloth seats, eight-way power for the driver, a multifunction steering wheel, air conditioning, wood-tone trim, remote start, and Intelligent Key with pushbutton ignition. An 8-inch touchscreen and a 7-inch driver display highlight the dashboard, supporting Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto®, Bluetooth®, voice control, and a six-speaker sound system with SiriusXM compatibility. You can appreciate those advantages on almost any trip!


Nissan helps safeguard your travels with sophisticated technologies such as lane-keeping assistance, rearview camera, front/rear automatic emergency braking, blind-spot monitoring, forward-collision warning, hill-start assistance, a rear-seat reminder, and more. You can elevate everyday driving with our excellent Altima SV! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

Our ES 350 brings a comfortable sense of refinement to the spacious cabin with a wood and leather-wrapped steering wheel with mounted controls, easy-to-read gauges, pushbutton start, power heated front leather seats with driver memory dual-zone climate control. With a stellar AM/FM/CD audio system with Bluetooth and SiriusXM radio capability, you can't help but smile as you glide to your destination in this elegant car.



Lexus has a reputation for safety and that holds firm with stability/traction control, ABS, tire pressure monitoring, and many airbags to safeguard you. This well-built car provides you with safety, comfort, and contentment. You'll know this is ES 350 sedan the right choice once you slip behind the wheel. Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

This well-equipped 2010 Ford F-150 XL is a rugged and capable pickup that's ready to take on any task. Powered by a robust 5.4L V8 engine and equipped with 4-wheel drive, this F-150 delivers impressive performance and off-road capability. With a spacious interior and seating for up to six, it's an ideal choice for work, play, or family adventures.

The exterior of this F-150 features a classic blue color that's both stylish and durable. The 17-inch gray steel wheels and rear step bumper add a touch of utility, while the keyless entry system and power windows provide added convenience. Inside, the cabin is well-appointed with features like air conditioning, power steering, and a AM/FM stereo system, ensuring a comfortable and enjoyable driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with this F-150 equipped with a suite of advanced safety technologies. Dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and electronic stability control work together to provide a secure and confident ride, no matter the conditions.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, navigating rough terrain, or simply commuting in style, this 2010 Ford F-150 XL is a versatile and capable pickup that's sure to impress. With its impressive capabilities, thoughtful features, and exceptional value, it's an opportunity you won't want to miss.

description: Experience the perfect blend of elegance and power with this Taffeta White 2012 Honda Accord Sedan SE, featuring a sophisticated 4-cylinder engine that promises an exhilarating yet smooth ride. Its automatic transmission ensures effortless driving, while the pristine Ivory interior invites you into a realm of comfort and style. With front-wheel drive enhancing its agility, this sedan is not just a vehicle but a gateway to remarkable journeys. CarFax No Accidents! Popular Options and Features Include: Comfort Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - Thats hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions. Heated driver seatback - Thats hot. Heated driver seatback provides more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower back pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in the heated driver seatback. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - Thats hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.Convenience Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.Safety and Security Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedals travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one. About Dublin Honda Not only are we Honda enthusiasts at Dublin Honda, were dedicated members of the local community. This 328i is truly a masterpiece of German engineering, blending power, style, and luxury into one exceptional package. Whether you're seeking the thrill of the open road or the refined elegance of a premium driving experience, this vehicle is sure to exceed your expectations.

Don't miss your chance to make this 2014 BMW 3 Series 328i your own. Schedule a test drive today and experience the difference that true craftsmanship and performance can make.

The Premium Plus Package further enhances the vehicle's capabilities, with features like Lane Guidance, 3-D Building Graphics, and the INFINITI Connection service.

description:
The 2016 Honda HR-V EX offers a smart blend of safety, versatility, and everyday comfort. Key safety features include a multi-angle back-up camera, Honda LaneWatch right-side camera, side-impact beams, multiple airbags throughout both rows, tire pressure monitoring, and rear child safety locks. On the outside, it stands out with 17-inch alloy wheels, fog lamps, LED brake lights, chrome-accented grille, heated power side mirrors, and a power sunroof. Inside, the cabin features heated front seats, a flexible 60/40 split Magic Seat for enhanced cargo versatility, automatic climate control, a driver information center, and HondaLink connectivity. Power comes from a responsive 1.8L i-VTEC engine paired with a CVT featuring Sport Mode and paddle shifters, while available all-wheel drive and four-wheel disc brakes enhance confidence in varied driving conditions.

Discover the power and versatility of this 2016 Ford F-150 XLT. With its robust 3.5L V6 Ti-VCT engine, 6-speed automatic transmission, and rear-wheel drive, this truck delivers an impressive blend of performance and efficiency, boasting an EPA-estimated 18 city/25 highway MPG.

GVWR: 6,150 lbs Payload Package
6 Speakers
AM/FM radio
Radio: AM/FM Stereo/Single-CD Player
SYNC Voice Recognition Communications
Air Conditioning
Power steering
Speed-sensing steering
Traction control
4-Wheel Disc Brakes
ABS brakes
Dual front impact airbags
Dual front side impact airbags

This F-150 XLT is more than just a workhorse; it's a versatile companion that can handle your toughest tasks with ease. The spacious interior, featuring a split folding rear seat, provides ample room for both passengers and cargo, while the 17-inch silver painted aluminum wheels and rear step bumper add a touch of style and functionality.

Equipped with a host of advanced safety features, including Electronic Stability Control, Brake Assist, and Occupant Sensing Airbag, this F-150 XLT offers the peace of mind you deserve. The delay-off headlights and fully automatic headlights ensure you'll always have the visibility you need, no matter the conditions.

Whether you're hauling heavy loads, navigating rough terrain, or simply enjoying the open road, this 2016 Ford F-150 XLT is ready to take on the challenge. With its impressive capabilities, thoughtful design, and uncompromising safety, it's the perfect choice for those who demand more from their truck.

At our dealership, we're committed to providing our customers with exceptional vehicles and unparalleled service. We invite you to experience the power and versatility of this 2016 Ford F-150 XLT for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this truck is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

description:
Here s what s great about a 2016 Audi Q5 3.0T Prestige:

Powerful Performance & All Weather Capability

Comes with a 3.0 liter supercharged V6 engine producing about 272 horsepower and 295 lb ft of torque.

Standard quattro all wheel drive system delivers excellent traction and stability in various driving conditions.

Towing capacity is up to 4,400 lbs when properly equipped, making it versatile for hauling small trailers or recreational gear.

Premium Interior & Feature-Rich Trim

The Prestige trim includes high-end features such as ventilated front seats, a premium sound system, adaptive xenon headlights with LED daytime running lights, and full leather upholstery.

Comfort amenities include power-adjustable driver s seat with memory settings, rear sunshades, panoramic roof options, and quality materials throughout the cabin for a refined driving experience.

Practicality & Space

Seating for five with generous front legroom and rear passenger space, accommodating adults comfortably.

Cargo space is about 29 cubic feet behind the rear seats and expands to around 57 cubic feet with the seats folded, providing versatility for luggage, groceries, or outdoor gear.

Value & Ownership Appeal

Combines Audi s reputation for luxury and engineering quality with strong performance, all-wheel drive, and a feature-rich interior.

The 3.0T Prestige trim offers a compelling mix of power, refinement, and utility, making it ideal for buyers who want a luxury SUV that is enjoyable to drive and practical for everyday use.

Under the hood, you'll find a spunky 2.0L Turbo I4 engine that produces a whopping 241 horsepower and a torque of 273 ft. lbs. It's like having a caffeinated squirrel on board, ready to zip you from 0 to 60 in no time. That's right; you can enjoy all this power while keeping your wallet happy.

The intuitive infotainment system keeps you connected with navigation, Bluetooth, and all the apps you need to pretend you're busy when you're really just Googling cat videos.

Safety? Oh, this baby has that covered too! With a suite of features that includes a rearview camera, parking sensors, and a host of airbags, you can drive with the confidence of a cat walking on a ledge (you know, minus the peril).

description:
Introducing the 2017 Chevrolet Bolt EV Premier, the ultimate electric vehicle for the modern driver. With its sleek and stylish design, this car will turn heads on the road. But it's not just about looks, the Bolt EV Premier boasts impressive performance and efficiency.

Equipped with a 60 kWh battery, this car has an impressive range of up to 238 miles on a single charge. Say goodbye to constant trips to the gas station and hello to a more sustainable and cost-effective driving experience.

Step inside and experience the spacious and luxurious interior of the Bolt EV Premier. With seating for up to five passengers and ample cargo space, this car is perfect for both daily commutes and road trips.

But that's not all, the Bolt EV Premier also comes with advanced technology features such as a 10.2-inch touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto compatibility, and a built-in 4G LTE Wi-Fi hotspot. Stay connected and entertained wherever you go.

Safety is a top priority with the Bolt EV Premier. It comes equipped with features like forward collision alert, lane keep assist, and rear cross traffic alert to help you stay safe on the road.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and advanced technology in this stunning 2017 Mazda Mazda3 Grand Touring. This meticulously maintained vehicle is a true standout, offering a captivating driving experience and a wealth of premium features that will elevate your daily commute.

Highlighted by its sleek black exterior, this Mazda3 Grand Touring is equipped with a host of cutting-edge technologies and premium amenities that set it apart from the competition. Key features include:

Text Brad Wilhite @ 256-203-0222
PREMIUM EQUIPMENT PACKAGE: Bi-LED Headlights with Auto Leveling, Mazda Navigation System, Heated Steering Wheel, Pivoting Adaptive Front-Lighting System, Steering Wheel Paddle Shifters, LED Combination Taillights, LED Daytime Running Lights, Auto-Dimming Interior Mirror with HomeLink
I-ACTIVSENSE SAFETY PACKAGE: High Beam Control, Lane Keep Assist, Traffic Sign Recognition, Mazda Radar Cruise Control, Smart Brake Support, Lane Departure Warning System

Powered by a responsive 2.5L I4 engine and paired with a smooth 6-speed automatic transmission, this Mazda3 delivers an exceptional blend of efficiency and performance. Boasting an impressive 28 MPG in the city and 37 MPG on the highway, it's the perfect companion for both your daily commute and weekend adventures.

The interior of this Mazda3 Grand Touring is equally impressive, with premium features such as a Bose Surround Sound System, Front Dual Zone Air Conditioning, Heads-Up Display, and Remote Keyless Entry. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob add a touch of elegance, while the power moonroof and heated front seats provide a luxurious driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Mazda3 Grand Touring equipped with an array of advanced i-ACTIVSENSE safety technologies. These include Lane Departure Warning System, Mazda Radar Cruise Control, Smart Brake Support, and Traffic Sign Recognition, ensuring you and your passengers can travel with confidence.

Whether you're looking for a stylish, feature-rich daily driver or a versatile companion for your active lifestyle, this 2017 Mazda Mazda3 Grand Touring is sure to impress. Experience the joy of driving with this exceptional vehicle. Schedule a test drive today and discover the difference for yourself.

The Enclave's 3.6L V6 engine and 9-speed automatic transmission deliver a smooth and responsive ride, while the front-wheel-drive configuration provides confident handling. With an EPA-estimated 18 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway, this Enclave offers impressive fuel efficiency for its size and capability.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior. The Buick Infotainment System with SiriusXM Satellite Radio keeps you entertained, while the dual-zone automatic climate control ensures everyone rides in comfort. The power driver's seat and heated front seats add an extra touch of luxury, and the 7-passenger seating provides ample room for the whole family.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like OnStar Guidance, Rear Parking Sensors, and a suite of airbags to give you peace of mind on the road. The Enclave's sleek exterior design is complemented by 18-inch painted aluminum wheels, a roof rack, and a power liftgate for added convenience.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or navigating your daily commute, this 2018 Buick Enclave Essence is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and capability all at an exceptional value.

description: Experience the Thrill of Precision Engineering with the 2018 BMW 3 Series 330i xDrive: Where Performance Meets Luxury in Every Drive Step into the world of refined driving with the 2018 BMW 3 Series 330i xDrive, a vehicle crafted for those who appreciate the perfect blend of power and elegance. The interior, a sanctuary of luxury, is designed to cater to your every need, offering an intuitive and immersive driving experience. The 2018 BMW 3 Series 330i xDrive is not just a vehicle it s a testament to the art of driving, tailored for those who demand more from their journey. description:
<p>Command the Road with the 2019 Dodge Challenger SXT: A Fusion of Power, Style, and Precision for the True Driving Enthusiast</p>
<p>Step into the world of high-octane performance with the 2019 Dodge Challenger SXT. This used masterpiece, cloaked in a striking Pitch Black Clearcoat, is engineered for those who crave the thrill of the drive. Beneath its muscular hood lies a formidable 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine, paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering seamless power and precision. The rear-wheel-drive configuration ensures an exhilarating connection to the road, perfect for the purist who values control and performance.</p>
<p>The Challenger SXT's exterior is a testament to its racing heritage, featuring performance tires and a rear spoiler that not only enhance its aggressive stance but also its aerodynamic efficiency. Inside, the driver-centric cockpit boasts a leather steering wheel and power-adjustable bucket seats, designed to provide comfort during every mile of your journey. Safety is paramount, with features like stability control, traction control, and a comprehensive airbag system ensuring peace of mind on every adventure.</p>
<p>For those who value a blend of classic American muscle and modern innovation, the 2019 Dodge Challenger SXT stands ready to deliver an unforgettable driving experience.</p>
<p>Be sure to call or visit ABC Nissan to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!</p>?

Hyundai leads the pack with advanced safety features, including blind-spot detection, a rearview camera, stability management, traction control, ABS, tire pressure monitoring, airbags, and more. OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Preferred Equipment Group 1LT Safety and Security Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision. Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.Technology and Telematics Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road. Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicles private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot. Motivated by a 2.4 Liter Tigershark 4 Cylinder that offers 180hp tethered to a 9 Speed Automatic transmission for fantastic adventures. This Front Wheel Drive SUV also scores nearly 31mpg on the highway while showing off upscale details like alloy wheels, bright roof rails, heated power mirrors, LED lighting, and fog lamps. Our Cherokee looks excellent with features like those!


A driver-friendly layout greets you in our Latitude Plus cabin with comfortable cloth/leather seats, eight-way power for the driver, a folding second row, a leather-wrapped steering wheel/shift knob, air conditioning, keyless entry/ignition, and clever Uconnect® infotainment technology. Highlights include a 7-inch touchscreen, Android Auto®/Apple CarPlay®, Bluetooth®, voice recognition, and a six-speaker sound system for your favorite tunes or talk.


Intelligent Jeep features such as a rearview camera, blind-spot monitoring, hill-start assistance, rear cross-traffic alert, rear parking sensors, tire pressure monitoring, and stability/traction control can add rewarding peace of mind to your travels. Exploring your world comes easy in our Cherokee Latitude Plus! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!

HUGE SALE IN PROGRESS........

The 2.0L 4-Cylinder MPI DOHC engine ensures a smooth yet spirited drive, perfect for navigating city streets or hitting the open road. Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and efficiency in the 2021 Kia Forte GT-Line. This exceptional sedan is a true standout, offering an unparalleled driving experience and a wealth of premium features that are sure to impress.

Boasting a striking exterior in Aurora Black, the Forte GT-Line commands attention with its sleek, aerodynamic design and alluring alloy wheels. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious, well-appointed cabin that exudes refinement. Indulge in the luxurious comfort of the 10-way power driver's seat, while the sunroof fills the interior with natural light, creating a truly inviting atmosphere.

SUNROOF

ALLOY WHEELS
BACKUP CAMERA
GAS-SAVER

The Forte GT-Line is equipped with a 2.0L 4-Cylinder MPI engine, delivering an impressive balance of power and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 29 mpg in the city and 40 mpg on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of the open road while keeping your fuel costs in check.

Cutting-edge technology is at your fingertips, thanks to the Forte's advanced infotainment system. Seamlessly connect your smartphone using Apple CarPlay or Android Auto, and immerse yourself in the rich, high-quality sound of the harman/kardon premium audio system. Stay connected and entertained on every journey.

The Forte GT-Line also boasts a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including a Rear Camera Display, Lane Departure Warning System, and Electronic Stability Control. These cutting-edge technologies work tirelessly to help keep you and your passengers secure, giving you the confidence to tackle the road ahead.

This 2021 Kia Forte GT-Line is a true standout in its class, offering a winning combination of style, performance, and technology. With its exceptional features, impressive fuel economy, and unbeatable value, it's the perfect choice for the discerning driver. Experience the thrill of driving the Forte GT-Line for yourself schedule a test drive today and discover the difference.

With its spacious interior, this FJ Cruiser comfortably seats five and has plenty of cargo space for all your gear. The exterior boasts a distinctive and bold design, with extra ground clearance and all-terrain tires for off-roading capabilities. An upscale performance machine, our bold 2011 BMW 5 Series 528i Sedan in Black provides a master class in motion. Powered by a thrilling 3.0 Liter 6 Cylinder offering 240hp paired with an 8 Speed STEPTRONIC Automatic transmission for confident acceleration and passing. BMW backs its high-end features with smart safety features such as stability/traction control ABS, tire-pressure monitoring, advanced dual-stage airbags, and a Head Protection System for both front and rear passengers. description:
2012 Toyota Prius
Price: $7,000
Mileage: 160,363
Color: White exterior / Beige interior
Title: Clean Title in hand
Seller: Private Party

Selling my 2012 Toyota Prius. If you are looking for a dependable commuter that gets incredible gas mileage (45-50 MPG), this is it. The car runs and drives great with no mechanical issues. I have taken good care of this vehicle, and it has been a perfect daily driver. The white paint is in decent shape for a 13 year old car, and the interior is clean and smoke-free.

Key Features

Fuel Economy: Consistently gets 45-50 MPG.

Maintenance: Regularly serviced; engine and hybrid system are strong.

Tires: All tires have approximately 50% tread life remaining plenty of miles left before you'll need replacements.

Tint: All windows tinted.

Cargo: Tons of room with the hatchback design and fold-down rear seats.

The Known Defects:
- One Key
- Some scratches to the paint (see pics for detail)
- Tire Light On: Needs a new TPMS sensor on one of the tires ($100-150). Doesn't affect the car, just means that it won't read low tire pressure there.

Price: $7,000 (Cash or Cashier's Check only). Sold As-Is by private seller.

This car is perfect for students, delivery drivers, or anyone looking to beat high gas prices. I am selling because I've upgraded to a larger vehicle for the family.

I won't be responding to low offers or trades.
