AutoNation Honda Roseville is pleased to be currently offering this 2013 Kia Optima LX with 100,327mi. This wonderfully fuel-efficient vehicle offers a supple ride, quick acceleration and superior styling without sacrificing MPGs. This low mileage Kia Optima has barely been touched. It's the next best thing to buying new. Look no further, you have found exactly what you've been looking for. More information about the 2013 Kia Optima: Compared to other mid-size sedans, the Kia Optima continues to stand out for several reasons. Showcasing Kia's more Euro-influenced design direction, the Optima has styling that's more exciting than that of other mid-size sedans, especially from the outside. And that design works out to be quite roomy on the inside. It's also one of the most fuel-efficient mid-size sedans, and it offers quite sporty performance considering its mileage numbers. The turbocharged engine in the SX in particular provides the power and acceleration of a V6 but the gas mileage of a four. The Optima is also a very strong value, with a few more features at each trim level than what's found in most comparable models. Kia's strong 10-year warranty on powertrain components remains another strong selling point. Interesting features of this model are strong acceleration in the SX, fuel-efficient powertrains, interior space, features and value for the money, strong warranty coverage, and Crisp, Euro-influenced styling

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, efficiency, and versatility in this 2014 Honda Civic EX. With its sleek blue exterior and well-appointed interior, this Civic is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting an impressive array of features, this Civic EX is equipped to meet your every need. Enjoy the convenience of the following:

160-Watt AM/FM/CD Audio System
Automatic Temperature Control
Power Moonroof
Rearview Camera
Steering Wheel-Mounted Audio Controls
Keyless Entry
Alloy Wheels

Under the hood, the 1.8L I4 SOHC 16V i-VTEC engine paired with a CVT transmission delivers an exceptional 30 city/39 highway MPG, making this Civic a true fuel-sipping champion.

Beyond its practical attributes, the Civic EX also exudes a refined and sophisticated presence. The well-appointed cabin features premium cloth seating, a leather-wrapped steering wheel, and thoughtful storage solutions to keep you organized on the go.

Safety is paramount, and this Civic EX delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including dual front and side impact airbags, ABS brakes, and Electronic Stability Control. You can drive with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

Whether you're commuting to the office, embarking on a weekend getaway, or simply running errands, this 2014 Honda Civic EX is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, efficiency, and cutting-edge technology make it a standout in the compact car segment.

This vehicle features a premium Ceramic Coating, applied for an additional $1,995, which includes a comprehensive 3-year warranty. This protective seal not only safeguards the exterior paint, headlights and alloy wheels from environmental damage but also protects the interior from spills, stains, rips, tears, burns and pet damage. Please note that Alcantara, seatbelts, and the steering wheel are not covered.

Beyond simply selling new cars, our dealership is also known for giving trade-ins a second chance on the road by carrying an excellent selection of used vehicles. Each vehicle we receive from a previous owner is thoroughly inspected to make sure it's fit to be driven, meaning you can count on a reliable vehicle when you shop at Honda of Libertyville. Here at Honda of Libertyville we're serving drivers in Vernon Hills, Lake Forest, Lake Bluff, Green Oaks, Mettawa, Mundelein, North Chicago, Waukegan, Lincolnshire, Lincolnwood, Highwood, Highland Park, Deerfield, Glencoe, Northbrook.

description:
This Flex is a rare find because it has only had one owner over the last decade, which tells you it was likely a well loved family staple rather than a rental or a fleet vehicle. Even though it is being sold as-is, the Flex has a cult following for a reason. It is basically a luxury lounge on wheels that offers more room and a smoother ride than almost any modern SUV in this price range.

Since this is the Limited trim, the interior is still impressively high end even by today's standards. It has the perforated leather seats that are both heated and cooled up front, along with a power folding third row that makes switching from passengers to cargo a one button job. It is also packed with the kind of features that make a long road trip actually enjoyable, like a premium Sony sound system and a blind spot monitoring system. You even get the power adjustable pedals and a power tailgate, which are those small conveniences that make a big difference when you are running errands.

It is a unique, spacious, and incredibly comfortable cruiser that gives you a lot of premium features and a clean one owner history for a very budget friendly price.

Check out this pre-owned 2014 Honda Civic Sedan we recently got in. You could spend more on fuel each month than on your vehicle payments, so why not consider one with exceptional fuel economy like this 2014 Honda Civic Sedan. One of the best things about this Honda Civic Sedan is that it has low, low mileage. It's ready for you to truly break it in. Driven by many, but adored by more, the Honda Civic Sedan LX is a perfect addition to any home. More information about the 2014 Honda Civic Sedan: For decades, the Civic has offered one of the best compact-car picks for those who want to keep their ownership costs low and plan to keep their cars a long time. The Civic is also one of the roomiest small sedans, with even better ride comfort and interior refinement this year. Discover the Versatile and Sophisticated 2015 Dodge Journey Crossroad

Boasting a sleek blue exterior and a spacious, well-appointed interior, this 2015 Dodge Journey Crossroad is a true standout in the crossover segment. With its powerful 3.6L V6 engine, flexible seating, and advanced technology features, this Journey is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Key features include:
Flexible Seating Group with 2nd-row 40/60 tilt and slide seat, 3rd-row 50/50 fold/reclining seat, and rear air conditioning
Navigation & Back-Up Camera Group with Garmin navigation system, SiriusXM Traffic, and ParkView rear backup camera
Popular Equipment Group with remote start, heated front seats, heated steering wheel, and more

The Journey Crossroad also offers a sunroof, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM satellite radio. With 25 highway MPG and a spacious, versatile interior, this crossover is ready to tackle your daily commute, weekend adventures, and everything in between.

Imagine the convenience of the available power liftgate, the comfort of the heated steering wheel on chilly mornings, and the peace of mind provided by the advanced safety features. The Dodge Journey Crossroad is a true family-friendly vehicle that combines style, capability, and technology in one impressive package.

Whether you're looking for a practical daily driver or a capable family hauler, this 2015 Dodge Journey Crossroad deserves your attention. With its impressive list of features and the confidence that comes with a local trade-in, this crossover is an exceptional value that's sure to impress. We invite you to schedule a test drive and experience the Dodge Journey Crossroad for yourself.

In conclusion, the 2015 Dodge Journey Crossroad offers a winning combination of style, versatility, and advanced technology. With its flexible seating, premium amenities, and efficient powertrain, this crossover is poised to exceed your expectations. Visit us today and let us show you why the Journey Crossroad should be your next vehicle.

With its spacious interior and advanced technology, the 2015 Ford Edge Titanium is the perfect choice for families, road trips, and daily commutes.

Under the hood, the 2015 Ford Edge Titanium boasts a powerful 3.5L V6 engine, delivering 280 horsepower and 250 lb-ft of torque. The 6-speed SelectShift automatic transmission allows for smooth and efficient shifting, while the all-wheel drive system provides enhanced traction and handling in any weather condition.

But the 2015 Ford Edge Titanium is not just about power - it's also packed with advanced technology. The SYNC with MyFord Touch infotainment system allows for hands-free control of your music, phone, and navigation. And with the available Sony Premium Audio System, you'll have concert-quality sound wherever you go.

Safety is a top priority in the 2015 Ford Edge Titanium. It comes equipped with features such as a rearview camera, blind spot monitoring, and cross-traffic alert to help you stay aware of your surroundings on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this top-of-the-line SUV. Come test drive the 2015 Ford Edge Titanium today and experience the perfect balance of style, performance, and technology. With its spacious interior, advanced features, and impressive power, the 2015 Ford Edge Titanium is the ultimate vehicle for those who demand the best.

Looking for a stylish and capable crossover that can handle your adventures with ease? Introducing the 2018 Dodge Journey Crossroad - a dynamic and versatile SUV that's ready to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a powerful 3.6L V6 engine paired with an efficient 6-speed automatic transmission and all-wheel drive, this Journey Crossroad delivers impressive performance and confidence on the road. Enjoy remarkable fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 24 mpg on the highway.

Key features of this well-equipped Dodge Journey Crossroad include:

Quick Order Package 28V Crossroad
Uconnect 3 with 8.4 display
Automatic tri-zone climate control
Leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob
Premium door trim with accent stitching
Power driver's seat
Rear air conditioning
Rear park assist
Rearview camera
Remote keyless entry

This Dodge Journey Crossroad also offers a wealth of advanced safety technologies to give you and your passengers peace of mind, including:

Dual front and side impact airbags
Electronic stability control
Traction control
4-wheel antilock disc brakes
Tire pressure monitoring system

With its spacious and versatile interior, the Journey Crossroad can accommodate up to seven passengers and their cargo with ease. The split-folding rear seats and available third-row seating provide the flexibility to handle your growing family's needs.

Stylishly appointed with a bold exterior design and a refined, well-appointed cabin, the 2018 Dodge Journey Crossroad is the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and convenience. Experience the difference for yourself - this exceptional crossover is ready to elevate your driving experience.

description:
Our nimble One Owner, Accident Free 2019 Ford Fiesta S Sedan is an absolute people pleaser in Oxford White! Fueled by an efficient 1.6 Liter 4 Cylinder that offers 120hp paired with a fun-to-drive 5 Speed Manual transmission. This Front Wheel Drive Fiesta is responsive and agile, and you will love that it scores nearly 35mpg on the highway! Hit the road in this Fiesta S and turn heads with a street-savvy design that boasts quad-beam halogen headlights, chrome grille accents, power mirrors, and solar-tinted glass.


The interior of our Fiesta S is packed with features you'll appreciate every day, including comfortable cloth seats, air conditioning, and the Ford Sync voice-activated infotainment system with a 4.2-inch display, Bluetooth®, App Link, and a six-speaker audio system with available Sirius XM so you can keep in touch and in tune with your world. Easy-to-use controls and versatile storage solutions also make this cabin a nice place to spend time.


Ford delivers peace of mind while driving since it comes standard with a backup camera, AdvanceTrac electronic stability control, advanced airbags, a tire-pressure monitoring system, ABS, and an SOS post-crash alert system. Show off sleek, sporty, and smart style each time you pull up in your Fiesta! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Top Notch Auto Sales Test Drive Towards Ownership!
